  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK780">
<l>purantārkaṇ ṇīrmalkac cākiṟpiṟ cākkā</l>
<l>ṭirantukōṭ ṭakka tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If (heroes) can so die as to fill with tears the eyes of their rulers, such a death deserves to be obtained even by begging.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
